fields.name: Help
fields.value:
[...] -> "..." is optional.
<...> -> Argument described by "..."
Valid "type"s: `GLOBAL_NATIVE`, `SPECIFIC_NATIVE`, `PERMISSION`, `GUILD`, `PARTY`, `SPECIFIC_HANDLED`, `DISCORD_TEXT`
Valid "identifier"s: Server Name, Permission, Guild UUID, Party UUID, Streamline Chat Channel Name, Discord Text Channel ID
